1
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:40,980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

2
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,990
=Episode 37=

3
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:51,260
Great Ancestor,

4
00:01:52,670 --> 00:01:53,580
are you alright?

5
00:01:58,470 --> 00:01:59,420
I know I was wrong.

6
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:00,300
I was too careless.

7
00:02:01,190 --> 00:02:02,190
I fell for Yan Ke's

8
00:02:02,190 --> 00:02:03,220
diversion stratagem.

9
00:02:04,390 --> 00:02:05,230
From now on,

10
00:02:06,420 --> 00:02:08,070
stay by Duan Xu's side at all times.

11
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:10,070
Don't let Yan Ke exploit a chance.

12
00:02:10,270 --> 00:02:11,110
Yes.

13
00:02:13,670 --> 00:02:14,510
But

14
00:02:15,740 --> 00:02:17,140
we can't track

15
00:02:17,140 --> 00:02:18,510
Yan Ke again.

16
00:02:21,550 --> 00:02:22,510
The elixir

17
00:02:23,420 --> 00:02:24,950
I gave Duan Xu just now

18
00:02:25,350 --> 00:02:26,390
can only temporarily ease

19
00:02:26,390 --> 00:02:27,460
his blood vomiting.

20
00:02:28,700 --> 00:02:29,540
But his five organs

21
00:02:32,230 --> 00:02:33,700
are damaged.

22
00:02:34,460 --> 00:02:35,830
I can't stop

23
00:02:38,350 --> 00:02:39,350
his body's decline.

24
00:02:52,267 --> 00:02:53,240
I'll return to the Void.

25
00:03:23,950 --> 00:03:24,790
The Spirits Lantern

26
00:03:24,790 --> 00:03:26,420
had become one with you.

27
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:29,790
If you kill me now,

28
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:32,110
you will only destroy

29
00:03:32,110 --> 00:03:33,230
the Spirits Lantern and me.

30
00:03:33,860 --> 00:03:35,180
Then your place as the Sovereign

31
00:03:35,510 --> 00:03:37,230
and the woman you can't have

32
00:03:37,790 --> 00:03:39,580
will be buried with me.

33
00:03:43,990 --> 00:03:45,620
I hold the Spirits Lantern's power.

34
00:03:46,230 --> 00:03:47,580
I can help you.

35
00:03:50,270 --> 00:03:51,230
Do I need help

36
00:03:51,230 --> 00:03:52,620
from a mere mortal?

37
00:03:53,830 --> 00:03:54,860
You can't control

38
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:56,270
the power of the Spirits Lantern.

39
00:03:57,140 --> 00:03:58,510
I need not kill you.

40
00:03:58,950 --> 00:04:00,900
Sooner or later,
you'll face annihilation.

41
00:04:03,110 --> 00:04:04,620
The war is deadlocked for now.

42
00:04:05,510 --> 00:04:07,005
If you can't use the Spirits Lantern,

43
00:04:07,016 --> 00:04:07,990
you can't defeat He Simu.

44
00:04:09,350 --> 00:04:10,620
Teach me to use spirit power;

45
00:04:11,390 --> 00:04:12,860
I'll use the Spirits Lantern for you.

46
00:04:13,620 --> 00:04:14,990
We'll bring down He Simu

47
00:04:15,790 --> 00:04:17,180
and kill Duan Xu.

48
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:25,910
I'll only teach you

49
00:04:26,670 --> 00:04:28,550
this cultivation method once.

50
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:31,030
Memorize it.

51
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:48,660
(Liang)

52
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:19,140
At the time,

53
00:05:19,990 --> 00:05:21,940
the vanguard squad led by Chenying

54
00:05:23,790 --> 00:05:25,620
was split down the middle
by Chong forces.

55
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:29,380
Chenying drew the enemy onto himself

56
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:32,710
to buy time for the main force

57
00:05:32,710 --> 00:05:33,710
to meet the attack.

58
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:36,620
But every man he took with him

59
00:05:39,150 --> 00:05:40,350
fell in battle,

60
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:44,350
and not one returned.

61
00:05:48,350 --> 00:05:49,190
This is

62
00:05:49,380 --> 00:05:51,300
the Liang's banner
Chenying died to keep.

63
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:08,940
This is all my fault.

64
00:06:11,350 --> 00:06:12,190
I should never

65
00:06:12,550 --> 00:06:14,060
have agreed to Chenying

66
00:06:14,230 --> 00:06:15,670
serving as the vanguard.

67
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:19,940
I brought this upon Chenying.

68
00:06:42,180 --> 00:06:43,020
Xu.

69
00:06:45,670 --> 00:06:46,940
Xu, are you alright?

70
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:15,740
(Zhaomu Pavilion)

71
00:07:15,740 --> 00:07:16,990
How are things in the Void now?

72
00:07:17,860 --> 00:07:20,180
Bai Sanxing led men through the Void

73
00:07:20,470 --> 00:07:21,213
and seized

74
00:07:21,224 --> 00:07:22,500
nearly all the puppet spirits.

75
00:07:23,670 --> 00:07:25,300
Bai Sanxing has been obedient lately.

76
00:07:26,956 --> 00:07:28,129
Thanks to you controlling him.

77
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:31,740
He longs to tear Yan Ke apart.

78
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:33,030
So, he spares no effort

79
00:07:33,030 --> 00:07:34,116
in catching puppet spirits.

80
00:07:36,836 --> 00:07:38,470
The Spirits Lantern
is still with Yan Ke.

81
00:07:39,550 --> 00:07:41,030
Luckily, he can't use it.

82
00:07:42,380 --> 00:07:43,380
There was an accident.

83
00:07:43,940 --> 00:07:44,820
He's found a way

84
00:07:44,820 --> 00:07:46,500
to use the Spirits Lantern indirectly.

85
00:07:47,470 --> 00:07:48,470
How could this happen?

86
00:07:49,536 --> 00:07:50,710
What do we do if this goes on?

87
00:07:51,550 --> 00:07:52,390
No need to worry.

88
00:07:53,550 --> 00:07:54,550
For Yan Ke to use

89
00:07:54,550 --> 00:07:55,470
the Spirits Lantern,

90
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:57,300
it will still take some time.

91
00:07:58,233 --> 00:08:00,099
Send some Spirit Officials
to the Mortal World

92
00:08:00,110 --> 00:08:01,380
and report back.

93
00:08:02,790 --> 00:08:03,710
The Void's affairs

94
00:08:04,180 --> 00:08:05,020
are in your charge.

95
00:08:05,663 --> 00:08:06,689
I need to enter seclusion.

96
00:08:07,180 --> 00:08:08,020
Enter seclusion?

97
00:08:08,380 --> 00:08:09,550
Why at a time like this?

98
00:08:12,740 --> 00:08:13,740
Gather the medicines

99
00:08:14,470 --> 00:08:15,310
on this list.

100
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,580
(Calculus Bovis, Borneol, Musk)

101
00:08:22,180 --> 00:08:23,030
How strange.

102
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:25,820
I can't feel anything,

103
00:08:27,420 --> 00:08:28,420
yet in my chest,

104
00:08:30,230 --> 00:08:31,180
it seems to ache.

105
00:08:43,540 --> 00:08:51,100
(Liang)

106
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:02,950
Xu.

107
00:09:03,900 --> 00:09:04,740
Xu.

108
00:09:07,470 --> 00:09:08,310
Xu.

109
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:10,280
Xu.

110
00:09:10,420 --> 00:09:11,360
Xiaoxiao just taught me

111
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,590
how to make a sugar figurine.

112
00:09:12,950 --> 00:09:13,900
Taste if it's sweet.

113
00:09:15,990 --> 00:09:16,930
Oh, right.

114
00:09:16,930 --> 00:09:18,590
I'll let Meng try some too.

115
00:09:22,990 --> 00:09:23,860
Han,

116
00:09:23,860 --> 00:09:25,260
I can never get this move right.

117
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:26,590
Show me again, will you?

118
00:09:27,860 --> 00:09:28,900
It has to reach this spot.

119
00:09:29,660 --> 00:09:30,710
This strike needs force.

120
00:09:31,350 --> 00:09:32,190
Like this.

121
00:09:32,710 --> 00:09:33,550
Xu,

122
00:09:34,990 --> 00:09:35,860
Xiaoxiao is back.

123
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:37,500
Let's get wine and meat pies.

124
00:09:37,830 --> 00:09:38,860
She loves meat pies.

125
00:09:39,199 --> 00:09:40,492
After she eats, she'll calm down.

126
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:41,430
Come on.

127
00:09:47,110 --> 00:09:48,140
Come on, Xu.

128
00:10:43,950 --> 00:10:44,860
(Foxy,)

129
00:10:45,780 --> 00:10:47,260
(I won't let you die like this.)

130
00:10:59,740 --> 00:11:00,590
Your Majesty,

131
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:01,663
Mr. Fang seeks an audience.

132
00:11:07,540 --> 00:11:09,350
Greetings, Your Majesty.

133
00:11:12,230 --> 00:11:14,350
Only Duan Xu didn't return to save me.

134
00:11:16,260 --> 00:11:18,020
By now, he should have arrived.

135
00:11:19,860 --> 00:11:21,140
Fang,

136
00:11:22,780 --> 00:11:24,380
why hasn't he returned?

137
00:11:26,710 --> 00:11:28,070
I know little of warfare.

138
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:29,230
I don't know.

139
00:11:30,470 --> 00:11:31,780
Perhaps some mishap

140
00:11:31,780 --> 00:11:32,740
delayed him.

141
00:11:33,190 --> 00:11:35,620
Duan Shunxi is the Marshal
of the Three Armies,

142
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:38,110
yet only he did not return.

143
00:11:43,860 --> 00:11:46,780
I know your talent.

144
00:11:48,310 --> 00:11:49,430
But, Fang,

145
00:11:50,660 --> 00:11:53,860
this world never lacks clever men.

146
00:11:54,860 --> 00:11:56,590
What it lacks is the right moment.

147
00:11:57,860 --> 00:11:59,430
You helped Jin save me.

148
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:00,830
So,

149
00:12:01,260 --> 00:12:02,100
I shall grant you

150
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:04,190
that moment.

151
00:12:05,350 --> 00:12:07,020
I will prepare an edict for you.

152
00:12:07,780 --> 00:12:09,230
You protected me,

153
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:12,110
so you are titled Marquis of Zhonghe

154
00:12:12,740 --> 00:12:15,110
and promoted
to Vice Military Commissioner

155
00:12:15,830 --> 00:12:16,990
and Vice Chancellor.

156
00:12:18,310 --> 00:12:20,740
You can decide when this edict

157
00:12:21,950 --> 00:12:22,830
is revealed.

158
00:12:24,950 --> 00:12:25,900
Thank you, Your Majesty.

159
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:29,710
Fang,

160
00:12:30,310 --> 00:12:31,500
do you truly want

161
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:32,900
to live as Duan Xu's shadow?

162
00:12:37,660 --> 00:12:39,430
(Duan Xu led Great Liang's elite)

163
00:12:39,590 --> 00:12:40,620
(and marched to Youzhou.)

164
00:12:40,990 --> 00:12:42,780
(Liang)
(After months of hard battle,)

165
00:12:43,110 --> 00:12:43,990
(now,)

166
00:12:43,990 --> 00:12:45,710
(of the 17 Prefectures,)

167
00:12:45,900 --> 00:12:47,540
(11 are retaken.)

168
00:12:47,860 --> 00:12:50,660
(Only Youzhou, Fengzhou, Huanzhou,)

169
00:12:50,950 --> 00:12:53,950
(Jingzhou, Yizhou, and Guizhou)

170
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:55,740
(Liang)
(are held by North Chong.)

171
00:12:55,990 --> 00:12:57,110
On the day I took command

172
00:12:57,110 --> 00:12:57,950
of the Three Armies,

173
00:12:58,950 --> 00:12:59,990
I made it clear to you.

174
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:01,860
What we seek

175
00:13:02,780 --> 00:13:03,990
is to win battles,

176
00:13:06,110 --> 00:13:07,430
but to safeguard

177
00:13:07,430 --> 00:13:08,270
our people.

178
00:13:08,990 --> 00:13:10,380
The Chong cavalry is fierce.

179
00:13:11,590 --> 00:13:12,950
They once relied

180
00:13:13,310 --> 00:13:14,620
on their cavalry to sweep

181
00:13:14,620 --> 00:13:15,470
all the way south.

182
00:13:17,110 --> 00:13:18,660
They harmed our people,

183
00:13:20,350 --> 00:13:22,020
seized the 17 Prefectures,

184
00:13:22,590 --> 00:13:23,950
and slaughtered our kin.

185
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:26,780
Now that we stand on this land,

186
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:29,900
we must not take one step back.

187
00:13:30,430 --> 00:13:31,990
Our army stands here

188
00:13:32,100 --> 00:13:33,810
to defend our own land

189
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:36,620
and honor the fallen souls.

190
00:13:49,740 --> 00:13:50,795
This is the Liang's banner

191
00:13:50,806 --> 00:13:52,780
Chenying died to keep.

192
00:13:54,140 --> 00:13:55,020
General,

193
00:13:55,020 --> 00:13:56,660
(Liang)
I want to fight on the field

194
00:13:56,660 --> 00:13:57,590
and defend our nation

195
00:13:57,590 --> 00:13:58,710
like you.

196
00:14:06,950 --> 00:14:07,990
Fight for our land!

197
00:14:08,230 --> 00:14:09,230
We must win!

198
00:14:10,190 --> 00:14:12,830
Fight for our land! We must win!

199
00:14:13,070 --> 00:14:15,710
Fight for our land! We must win!

200
00:14:15,950 --> 00:14:18,540
Fight for our land! We must win!

201
00:14:19,190 --> 00:14:22,020
Fight for our land! We must win!

202
00:14:35,260 --> 00:14:41,500
(Liang)

203
00:14:47,710 --> 00:14:49,310
Your Majesty, you cherish the people.

204
00:14:49,780 --> 00:14:50,710
You've raised

205
00:14:50,710 --> 00:14:51,900
pillars of the realm.

206
00:14:52,426 --> 00:14:53,609
Now, policies grace the court;

207
00:14:53,620 --> 00:14:54,753
the Chong forces are quelled.

208
00:14:55,310 --> 00:14:56,150
Prince Jin

209
00:14:56,310 --> 00:14:57,350
will surely not fail

210
00:14:57,350 --> 00:14:58,350
your hopes.

211
00:14:59,620 --> 00:15:01,430
Leave me alone for a while.

212
00:15:34,590 --> 00:15:35,660
Father,

213
00:15:37,950 --> 00:15:39,830
your most timid son

214
00:15:42,470 --> 00:15:43,860
has done all he could.

215
00:15:46,230 --> 00:15:47,310
In this lifetime,

216
00:15:50,230 --> 00:15:52,110
I could not live to see Great Liang

217
00:15:54,660 --> 00:15:56,260
reclaim all lost lands.

218
00:15:58,660 --> 00:15:59,830
I can only die

219
00:16:03,230 --> 00:16:04,070
with regret.

220
00:16:33,660 --> 00:16:35,990
(Three days
after the order returned to Nandu,)

221
00:16:36,189 --> 00:16:37,602
(the Emperor of Liang passed away.)

222
00:16:37,613 --> 00:16:39,076
(The New Emperor ascends the throne.)

223
00:16:40,070 --> 00:16:41,020
(At this time,)

224
00:16:41,020 --> 00:16:42,260
(on the north bank, Duan Xu)

225
00:16:42,430 --> 00:16:44,780
(led the Great Liang Army past Youzhou)

226
00:16:45,110 --> 00:16:46,260
(and smoothly retook)

227
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:50,500
(Fengzhou, Huanzhou, Jingzhou,
Yizhou and Guizhou.)

228
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:55,900
Long live Your Majesty.

229
00:17:15,060 --> 00:17:15,950
Young Master, bad news!

230
00:17:16,190 --> 00:17:17,030
Bad news!

231
00:17:17,910 --> 00:17:18,750
Young Master,

232
00:17:19,007 --> 00:17:20,147
thieves broke into the house.

233
00:17:20,923 --> 00:17:22,239
None of the valuables were taken,

234
00:17:22,390 --> 00:17:23,820
but the study was turned upside down.

235
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:36,190
(The Analects)
I will prepare an edict for you.

236
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:39,060
You protected me,

237
00:17:39,710 --> 00:17:41,990
so you are titled Marquis of Zhonghe

238
00:17:42,630 --> 00:17:44,710
and promoted
to Vice Military Commissioner

239
00:17:45,430 --> 00:17:46,710
and Vice Chancellor.

240
00:17:47,990 --> 00:17:50,430
You can decide when this edict

241
00:17:51,580 --> 00:17:52,580
is revealed.

242
00:17:56,863 --> 00:17:57,876
(The late emperor's edict)

243
00:17:59,780 --> 00:18:00,630
(is gone.)

244
00:18:02,230 --> 00:18:03,190
You've been

245
00:18:03,870 --> 00:18:05,340
the youngest Top Scholar of all

246
00:18:05,340 --> 00:18:06,820
since Great Liang was founded.

247
00:18:07,910 --> 00:18:10,630
Ever fearful, yet caring for the people,

248
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:13,630
you bear the virtue of Yan Hui.

249
00:18:14,950 --> 00:18:15,790
Duan Xu

250
00:18:16,190 --> 00:18:17,630
has a noble family behind him

251
00:18:17,950 --> 00:18:19,340
and countless shadows.

252
00:18:20,340 --> 00:18:21,580
Your chance

253
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:23,670
comes but this once.

254
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:26,580
This decree of mine

255
00:18:26,990 --> 00:18:29,540
will raise you high
to fulfill your aims.

256
00:18:30,820 --> 00:18:33,430
After Jin ascends the throne,

257
00:18:34,230 --> 00:18:35,230
you will become

258
00:18:36,190 --> 00:18:37,670
his most capable minister.

259
00:18:41,260 --> 00:18:43,190
But to this decree,

260
00:18:43,740 --> 00:18:45,340
I must add one more clause:

261
00:18:46,580 --> 00:18:48,470
Duan Xu failed to arrive in time,

262
00:18:49,060 --> 00:18:50,910
harboring negligence
and treasonous intent.

263
00:18:51,870 --> 00:18:53,950
Upon his return to Nandu,

264
00:18:54,470 --> 00:18:55,990
he must be stripped of his command

265
00:18:57,230 --> 00:18:58,300
and executed.

266
00:18:59,910 --> 00:19:00,990
In all of Great Liang,

267
00:19:02,060 --> 00:19:03,060
he is

268
00:19:03,060 --> 00:19:04,390
the most exceptional general.

269
00:19:06,910 --> 00:19:08,020
But this blade

270
00:19:09,390 --> 00:19:11,230
must stay in my hand.

271
00:19:12,430 --> 00:19:13,270
From this day on,

272
00:19:14,500 --> 00:19:17,230
it must rest with the new emperor.

273
00:19:34,230 --> 00:19:35,070
Mr. Fang.

274
00:19:44,230 --> 00:19:45,070
Miss Duan.

275
00:19:46,540 --> 00:19:47,380
Mr. Fang,

276
00:19:51,150 --> 00:19:53,150
we made extra dumplings at home.

277
00:19:53,910 --> 00:19:56,870
Since you have no family in Nandu,

278
00:19:57,670 --> 00:19:58,510
I wanted

279
00:19:59,260 --> 00:20:01,260
to send some to your place.

280
00:20:04,430 --> 00:20:06,230
- Great.
- Good.

281
00:20:09,900 --> 00:20:17,580
(Yueran Fragrance)

282
00:20:23,340 --> 00:20:24,740
When unrest broke out in Nandu,

283
00:20:25,580 --> 00:20:27,740
I received an anonymous letter.

284
00:20:29,950 --> 00:20:31,580
Thanks to the warning in it,

285
00:20:32,740 --> 00:20:34,740
the Duan clan avoided the turmoil.

286
00:20:39,630 --> 00:20:40,870
Was that letter

287
00:20:43,340 --> 00:20:44,500
from you?

288
00:20:53,230 --> 00:20:54,070
I...

289
00:20:54,670 --> 00:20:56,020
I recognized your handwriting.

290
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:04,430
So, Miss Duan,

291
00:21:05,710 --> 00:21:07,190
that's why you brought me dumplings.

292
00:21:15,870 --> 00:21:16,820
Actually,

293
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:19,300
you and Xu must be

294
00:21:20,260 --> 00:21:21,100
quite close, right?

295
00:21:23,670 --> 00:21:25,260
In this world,

296
00:21:27,430 --> 00:21:28,740
others are the ones who owe Xu.

297
00:21:30,540 --> 00:21:31,950
He has never owed anyone.

298
00:21:39,100 --> 00:21:39,950
However,

299
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:44,300
soon, he will owe me.

300
00:21:48,230 --> 00:21:49,740
Then I'll thank you for him,

301
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:51,430
Fang Xianye.

302
00:21:55,710 --> 00:21:56,550
Xu.

303
00:21:56,870 --> 00:21:57,740
Xu.

304
00:22:05,950 --> 00:22:06,790
What is it?

305
00:22:07,470 --> 00:22:09,060
I can't tie this.

306
00:22:21,470 --> 00:22:22,390
In that case,

307
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:24,740
could you call me brother?

308
00:22:29,990 --> 00:22:31,670
You have not joined my family.

309
00:22:32,430 --> 00:22:33,270
I...

310
00:22:33,990 --> 00:22:34,830
You are

311
00:22:35,190 --> 00:22:36,390
taking advantage of me.

312
00:22:37,730 --> 00:22:39,300
You are not my brother.

313
00:22:51,100 --> 00:22:51,940
Brother.

314
00:22:59,540 --> 00:23:00,910
Your essays

315
00:23:01,190 --> 00:23:03,580
are the finest in the realm.

316
00:23:04,390 --> 00:23:06,470
One day, you'll be the Top Scholar.

317
00:23:15,660 --> 00:23:19,940
(Duan Shunxi)

318
00:23:34,430 --> 00:23:37,710
Prince Ji and Prince Su

319
00:23:38,190 --> 00:23:39,300
raised troops for treason.

320
00:23:40,020 --> 00:23:41,500
Behind them stood

321
00:23:41,500 --> 00:23:42,430
Duke Pei

322
00:23:42,430 --> 00:23:44,300
and Chancellor Du.

323
00:23:45,340 --> 00:23:46,630
As officials of the court,

324
00:23:47,190 --> 00:23:48,430
they should serve the realm,

325
00:23:48,430 --> 00:23:49,710
yet they turned to treason.

326
00:23:50,740 --> 00:23:53,230
Bring up the guilty Yao Jianhe.

327
00:23:53,430 --> 00:23:54,910
The late emperor's edict is here.

328
00:24:03,950 --> 00:24:05,740
The late emperor's edict is here.

329
00:24:05,980 --> 00:24:08,580
(Decree)

330
00:24:08,580 --> 00:24:09,420
This edict represents

331
00:24:09,670 --> 00:24:10,710
the late emperor.

332
00:24:12,580 --> 00:24:14,260
(Decree to Fang Ji and Duan Xu)

333
00:24:23,390 --> 00:24:24,383
The late emperor's edict:

334
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:26,786
Fang Ji earned merit
protecting the Emperor.

335
00:24:27,096 --> 00:24:29,429
He is made Vice Military Commissioner
and Vice Chancellor.

336
00:24:29,630 --> 00:24:31,430
Duan Xu failed
in protecting the Emperor.

337
00:24:31,526 --> 00:24:32,712
He harbored treasonous intent.

338
00:24:33,150 --> 00:24:34,100
He must be put to death.

339
00:24:34,500 --> 00:24:36,780
It bears the late emperor's seal.

340
00:24:36,950 --> 00:24:37,820
It's absolutely true.

341
00:24:38,430 --> 00:24:39,300
How dare you!

342
00:24:39,740 --> 00:24:41,670
Marshal Duan commands the Three Armies.

343
00:24:41,990 --> 00:24:43,630
He is still fighting
for us at the front.

344
00:24:43,930 --> 00:24:44,780
Your Majesty,

345
00:24:44,780 --> 00:24:46,100
you should execute

346
00:24:46,230 --> 00:24:47,580
such a treasonous rebel

347
00:24:47,820 --> 00:24:48,660
at once.

348
00:24:48,820 --> 00:24:49,660
How dare you!

349
00:24:49,830 --> 00:24:51,163
This is the late emperor's edict.

350
00:24:51,260 --> 00:24:52,100
Do you want

351
00:24:52,300 --> 00:24:53,710
to defy the imperial edict?

352
00:25:06,430 --> 00:25:07,270
Xianye,

353
00:25:08,100 --> 00:25:09,060
if you had such an edict

354
00:25:09,780 --> 00:25:12,300
to aid the rightful ruler
and strike rebels,

355
00:25:12,670 --> 00:25:14,630
why not present it
to His Majesty sooner?

356
00:25:14,990 --> 00:25:17,150
This was your perfect chance

357
00:25:17,150 --> 00:25:17,990
to rise to power.

358
00:25:17,990 --> 00:25:18,830
Mentor,

359
00:25:19,870 --> 00:25:21,150
why are you doing this to me?

360
00:25:29,100 --> 00:25:29,990
Your Majesty,

361
00:25:30,540 --> 00:25:31,780
I'd like to report a matter.

362
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:33,740
Please punish me.

363
00:25:36,540 --> 00:25:37,390
Yao Jianhe ordered me

364
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:39,100
to forge

365
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:40,390
this edict.

366
00:25:40,670 --> 00:25:41,510
Fang Xianye!

367
00:25:43,820 --> 00:25:45,340
Yao Jianhe was my honored teacher.

368
00:25:45,820 --> 00:25:47,390
I could not bear to see him suffer,

369
00:25:47,670 --> 00:25:49,340
so I had no choice but to obey.

370
00:25:49,710 --> 00:25:50,820
What utter nonsense.

371
00:25:51,020 --> 00:25:51,860
Fang Xianye!

372
00:25:51,990 --> 00:25:53,020
You...

373
00:25:53,630 --> 00:25:55,340
You held the late emperor's edict

374
00:25:55,446 --> 00:25:56,540
yet refused to hand it over,

375
00:25:56,670 --> 00:25:59,230
joining Duan Xu in defying
the imperial edict.

376
00:25:59,950 --> 00:26:00,790
I am guilty.

377
00:26:01,390 --> 00:26:03,300
I shouldn't have followed

378
00:26:03,539 --> 00:26:04,625
vile courtiers into treason

379
00:26:04,870 --> 00:26:06,630
just because of the mentorial bond.

380
00:26:38,580 --> 00:26:40,100
Since the late emperor passed away,

381
00:26:41,430 --> 00:26:43,020
he has visited my dreams nightly,

382
00:26:43,580 --> 00:26:45,950
fiercely rebuking me
for framing loyal officials.

383
00:26:46,870 --> 00:26:48,060
I was consumed by dread

384
00:26:48,230 --> 00:26:49,870
and resolved to destroy
the forged edict,

385
00:26:50,150 --> 00:26:51,820
yet it was stolen by the rebel faction.

386
00:26:56,260 --> 00:26:57,100
Your Majesty,

387
00:26:57,230 --> 00:26:58,670
I dare not deceive you.

388
00:26:59,300 --> 00:27:00,670
Nor can I face my honored teacher.

389
00:27:01,100 --> 00:27:01,950
Your Majesty,

390
00:27:02,230 --> 00:27:03,350
please purge the conspirators

391
00:27:03,580 --> 00:27:05,100
and restore the order of the court.

392
00:27:06,100 --> 00:27:06,990
You insolent fool!

393
00:27:07,500 --> 00:27:08,740
You insolent fool!

394
00:27:09,020 --> 00:27:09,910
Fang Xianye!

395
00:27:10,100 --> 00:27:11,820
Have you lost your mind?

396
00:27:24,500 --> 00:27:26,870
I have committed high treason

397
00:27:27,870 --> 00:27:29,630
by trying to ruin a loyal subject.

398
00:27:30,910 --> 00:27:32,300
My crime is beyond pardon.

399
00:27:36,470 --> 00:27:38,100
Before the late emperor's spirit,

400
00:27:39,540 --> 00:27:41,020
I am too ashamed.

401
00:27:41,950 --> 00:27:43,710
Only death remains for me.

402
00:27:44,670 --> 00:27:45,510
Fang Ji!

403
00:27:53,540 --> 00:27:54,470
This...

404
00:28:01,020 --> 00:28:01,860
Xianye!

405
00:28:07,150 --> 00:28:08,780
(If I make this edict a forged one,)

406
00:28:09,740 --> 00:28:10,950
(Duan Xu may be spared.)

407
00:28:15,100 --> 00:28:15,940
(If I die,)

408
00:28:16,670 --> 00:28:17,990
(there will be no witnesses left.)

409
00:28:20,710 --> 00:28:21,550
(Duan Shunxi,)

410
00:28:23,300 --> 00:28:24,780
(you still owe me in the end.)

411
00:28:28,910 --> 00:28:30,430
Drag this rebel out

412
00:28:30,780 --> 00:28:32,780
for the ultimate punishment.

413
00:28:32,780 --> 00:28:33,620
Yes.

414
00:28:53,230 --> 00:28:54,070
Put it here.

415
00:28:54,950 --> 00:28:55,790
Careful.

416
00:28:56,160 --> 00:28:57,020
These are

417
00:28:57,020 --> 00:28:57,990
Xu's favorite books.

418
00:28:58,300 --> 00:28:59,340
Don't damage any of them.

419
00:28:59,670 --> 00:29:00,510
Yes.

420
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:04,950
Jingyuan.

421
00:29:04,950 --> 00:29:05,790
Come in.

422
00:29:07,580 --> 00:29:08,540
Keep tidying up.

423
00:29:08,540 --> 00:29:09,380
All right.

424
00:29:14,820 --> 00:29:15,660
Father,

425
00:29:15,990 --> 00:29:17,230
what did you want with me?

426
00:29:19,580 --> 00:29:20,870
What has pleased you so today?

427
00:29:22,020 --> 00:29:23,780
Nandu has been stable lately.

428
00:29:23,780 --> 00:29:25,060
Xu fought at the frontier.

429
00:29:25,500 --> 00:29:27,780
He'll return
with illustrious military merit.

430
00:29:28,300 --> 00:29:30,190
Now, even his greatest rival,

431
00:29:30,540 --> 00:29:31,870
Fang Xianye, is dead.

432
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:34,390
Someone who should've died long ago

433
00:29:34,670 --> 00:29:36,820
somehow clung to life till now.

434
00:29:38,630 --> 00:29:40,500
My wish is fulfilled.

435
00:29:41,230 --> 00:29:42,710
Now, it is time to settle your future.

436
00:29:43,470 --> 00:29:44,310
Come.

437
00:29:44,630 --> 00:29:45,470
On this list

438
00:29:46,150 --> 00:29:47,910
are eligible noble scions of Nandu,

439
00:29:48,670 --> 00:29:49,850
such as the Grand Master's son

440
00:29:50,300 --> 00:29:52,500
and the Duke of Lu's son.

441
00:29:53,230 --> 00:29:54,470
Though I have retired,

442
00:29:55,060 --> 00:29:57,060
with your Xu in Nandu,

443
00:29:57,430 --> 00:29:59,300
the Duan clan
is still of illustrious standing.

444
00:30:00,020 --> 00:30:01,260
You are my legitimate daughter.

445
00:30:02,206 --> 00:30:03,500
You must marry into a great house

446
00:30:03,511 --> 00:30:04,921
to carry on the Duan clan's honor.

447
00:30:05,780 --> 00:30:07,340
Look over these young men first.

448
00:30:07,710 --> 00:30:08,550
If one suits you,

449
00:30:08,710 --> 00:30:10,470
I'll arrange a marriage proposal.

450
00:30:21,060 --> 00:30:21,900
I don't like them.

451
00:30:22,630 --> 00:30:23,780
You have not even looked yet.

452
00:30:23,780 --> 00:30:24,870
How can you dislike them?

453
00:30:26,190 --> 00:30:27,030
I said it already.

454
00:30:27,950 --> 00:30:28,790
I don't like them.

455
00:30:29,870 --> 00:30:31,060
Was taking over Xu's life

456
00:30:31,060 --> 00:30:31,900
not enough for you?

457
00:30:32,530 --> 00:30:33,618
Now, you want to take over

458
00:30:33,629 --> 00:30:34,396
my life as well?

459
00:30:38,580 --> 00:30:39,420
You...

460
00:30:47,780 --> 00:30:49,240
Suddenly, I miss my younger sister.

461
00:30:50,230 --> 00:30:51,323
You are very much like her.

462
00:30:55,630 --> 00:30:56,470
Me?

463
00:31:00,740 --> 00:31:04,360
♪In silence, I gaze at you♪

464
00:31:04,560 --> 00:31:08,290
♪My hand hangs and then falls♪

465
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:12,200
♪Let what stays unsaid pass♪

466
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:16,450
♪Why torture each other like this?♪

467
00:31:16,730 --> 00:31:20,000
♪My wish might be♪

468
00:31:20,220 --> 00:31:23,600
♪Scattering like ripples♪

469
00:31:23,910 --> 00:31:29,990
♪With a gust of wind,
they fade like a dream♪

470
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:35,620
♪Daylight fades into ash♪

471
00:31:35,620 --> 00:31:39,580
(Yueran Fragrance)

472
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:42,920
♪For the rest of my life♪

473
00:31:43,870 --> 00:31:44,710
Jingyuan.

474
00:31:46,470 --> 00:31:47,630
May you find a worthy husband,

475
00:31:49,150 --> 00:31:50,430
be blessed with many children,

476
00:31:53,100 --> 00:31:54,060
and live a happy life.

477
00:31:54,570 --> 00:31:59,640
♪Collapse piece by piece♪

478
00:31:59,740 --> 00:32:00,580
Promise me,

479
00:32:03,260 --> 00:32:04,100
all right?

480
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:10,290
♪And did not dare draw near again♪

481
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:13,230
♪Leaving all behind♪

482
00:32:13,530 --> 00:32:18,000
♪The sudden pause of words unsaid♪

483
00:32:18,350 --> 00:32:21,760
♪How I long
to hold that silhouette close♪

484
00:32:22,170 --> 00:32:25,680
♪After waking up, we walk back-to-back♪

485
00:32:27,580 --> 00:32:28,420
Milady,

486
00:32:29,230 --> 00:32:30,300
why are you crying?

487
00:32:31,340 --> 00:32:32,860
(Yueran Fragrance)

488
00:32:33,730 --> 00:32:37,720
♪How I long
to hold that silhouette close♪

489
00:32:37,860 --> 00:32:41,320
♪After waking up, we walk back-to-back♪

490
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:45,250
♪Watching all that is unfinished♪

491
00:32:45,430 --> 00:32:50,480
♪Fade away♪

492
00:32:57,820 --> 00:32:58,660
I have met him

493
00:32:59,710 --> 00:33:01,710
fewer than five times.

494
00:33:04,300 --> 00:33:05,150
Why?

495
00:33:05,150 --> 00:33:08,360
♪In the end,
love is the hardest to resist♪

496
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:11,540
Why does he grieve me so deeply?

497
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:15,290
♪Alone, I gather them up♪

498
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:19,730
♪Like petals in the spring sun♪

499
00:33:20,270 --> 00:33:23,750
♪Till the past falls still again♪

500
00:33:25,100 --> 00:33:27,950
(Yueran Fragrance)

501
00:33:27,950 --> 00:33:36,580
♪The wind returns with my dreams♪

502
00:33:36,580 --> 00:33:39,420
(Liang)

503
00:34:17,220 --> 00:34:18,060
Unexpectedly,

504
00:34:18,540 --> 00:34:19,990
our long-held wish is near.

505
00:34:21,870 --> 00:34:23,540
So many years have passed.

506
00:34:25,020 --> 00:34:26,540
Back then, I drew you into this cause,

507
00:34:27,470 --> 00:34:28,310
yet in the end,

508
00:34:28,700 --> 00:34:29,580
I asked you instead,

509
00:34:30,910 --> 00:34:31,750
"In this world,"

510
00:34:32,990 --> 00:34:34,323
"can things truly go as we hoped?"

511
00:34:39,470 --> 00:34:40,310
You said,

512
00:34:41,620 --> 00:34:42,580
"It doesn't matter."

513
00:34:44,100 --> 00:34:45,140
"We need only try first."

514
00:34:46,390 --> 00:34:47,230
"The deepest night"

515
00:34:47,700 --> 00:34:48,540
"heralds the dawn."

516
00:34:50,830 --> 00:34:51,830
It feels like yesterday.

517
00:34:54,220 --> 00:34:55,060
Xianye.

518
00:34:57,950 --> 00:34:59,020
I spent a lifetime alone.

519
00:34:59,756 --> 00:35:00,742
I lost my parents young.

520
00:35:01,180 --> 00:35:02,270
I had only one confidant

521
00:35:02,660 --> 00:35:03,999
and a girl that I loved for years

522
00:35:04,390 --> 00:35:05,990
and never let her know.

523
00:35:11,060 --> 00:35:12,310
I'll leave the future dawn

524
00:35:13,270 --> 00:35:14,660
for you to see.

525
00:35:17,660 --> 00:35:18,500
I shall

526
00:35:19,060 --> 00:35:19,900
leave first.

527
00:35:35,220 --> 00:35:36,060
Fang Ji.

528
00:35:41,020 --> 00:35:41,860
Fang Ji.

529
00:35:42,790 --> 00:35:43,630
Fang Ji!

530
00:35:55,270 --> 00:35:56,790
Marshal, urgent word from Nandu.

531
00:36:00,950 --> 00:36:01,910
Marshal,

532
00:36:01,910 --> 00:36:02,750
a message from Nandu.

533
00:36:03,270 --> 00:36:04,536
Prince Jin has taken the throne.

534
00:36:09,750 --> 00:36:10,660
Mr. Fang is dead.

535
00:36:28,860 --> 00:36:32,340
(The forerunner met his end
in the wild.)

536
00:36:35,830 --> 00:36:36,910
Chaos broke out in Nandu.

537
00:36:37,270 --> 00:36:38,580
Prince Su and Prince Ji rebelled.

538
00:36:39,060 --> 00:36:40,580
The late emperor called for aid.

539
00:36:40,790 --> 00:36:41,700
But the court messenger

540
00:36:41,700 --> 00:36:42,750
never reached here.

541
00:36:43,470 --> 00:36:44,700
Now, His Majesty has learned

542
00:36:45,060 --> 00:36:46,220
that the Pei faction

543
00:36:46,430 --> 00:36:47,540
framed you on purpose.

544
00:36:47,860 --> 00:36:48,820
(To Shunxi, From Xianye)

545
00:36:48,870 --> 00:36:50,350
Fang Xianye, Vice Minister of Revenue,

546
00:36:50,830 --> 00:36:52,390
drafted a fake edict to accuse you.

547
00:36:53,470 --> 00:36:54,500
After it was exposed,

548
00:36:55,923 --> 00:36:57,149
he died by striking a pillar.

549
00:37:04,540 --> 00:37:05,380
(Shunxi,)

550
00:37:06,910 --> 00:37:07,910
(Nandu is now at peace.)

551
00:37:08,540 --> 00:37:09,500
(No need to worry.)

552
00:37:11,060 --> 00:37:12,990
(I have not seen you in many years.)

553
00:37:13,910 --> 00:37:14,990
(How brief a life is.)

554
00:37:15,317 --> 00:37:16,417
(We've parted for so long.)

555
00:37:17,950 --> 00:37:19,396
(Our paths differ with the same aim.)

556
00:37:20,430 --> 00:37:21,500
(Now, my task is done.)

557
00:37:22,270 --> 00:37:23,430
(Death is enough for me.)

558
00:37:24,613 --> 00:37:25,626
(It concerns no one else.)

559
00:37:26,290 --> 00:37:27,576
(Life is full of uncertainties.)

560
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:30,540
(When you reclaim the land,)

561
00:37:31,700 --> 00:37:33,270
(please pour wine to tell me.)

562
00:37:41,580 --> 00:37:42,420
Marshal.

563
00:37:44,350 --> 00:37:45,190
Marshal!

564
00:37:46,580 --> 00:37:47,420
Marshal.

565
00:37:49,180 --> 00:37:50,020
Physician!

566
00:37:50,470 --> 00:37:51,830
(I lived a lonely life.)

567
00:37:52,870 --> 00:37:53,710
(You are)

568
00:37:54,220 --> 00:37:55,060
(my only kin,)

569
00:37:55,830 --> 00:37:56,670
(my dearest friend,)

570
00:37:57,700 --> 00:37:59,180
(and my true confidant.)

571
00:38:00,220 --> 00:38:01,990
(From: Xianye)

572
00:38:14,020 --> 00:38:15,220
This time, I can do no more.

573
00:38:16,270 --> 00:38:17,790
I've sent word to Great Ancestor.

574
00:38:18,350 --> 00:38:19,220
I only hope she can

575
00:38:20,060 --> 00:38:21,430
bring the medicine back asap.

576
00:38:23,620 --> 00:38:24,460
Great Ancestor.

577
00:39:26,910 --> 00:39:27,910
You nearly died.

578
00:39:31,350 --> 00:39:32,190
Simu.

579
00:39:35,100 --> 00:39:35,940
Simu,

580
00:39:38,060 --> 00:39:39,020
Fang Xianye...

581
00:39:40,500 --> 00:39:41,700
Fang Xianye took his own life.

582
00:39:43,580 --> 00:39:44,470
Take me to him.

583
00:39:46,060 --> 00:39:47,100
I need to see him.

584
00:40:17,060 --> 00:40:17,950
Duan Shunxi.

585
00:40:28,950 --> 00:40:30,950
When I was taken to North Chong,

586
00:40:35,310 --> 00:40:37,430
my father forced Fang Xianye back

587
00:40:40,870 --> 00:40:41,910
to stand in for me.

588
00:40:43,350 --> 00:40:44,350
After I returned,

589
00:40:47,100 --> 00:40:48,910
my father nearly silenced him.

590
00:40:50,790 --> 00:40:52,910
He had every reason
to hate the Duan clan,

591
00:40:54,310 --> 00:40:55,270
but he never once

592
00:40:55,270 --> 00:40:56,110
mentioned it to me.

593
00:40:57,180 --> 00:40:58,700
If we had not shared the same cause,

594
00:41:00,830 --> 00:41:02,060
Fang Xianye and I

595
00:41:05,060 --> 00:41:06,620
should have been enemies.

596
00:41:10,660 --> 00:41:11,830
I had always thought

597
00:41:14,270 --> 00:41:15,790
that once the war was over,

598
00:41:18,100 --> 00:41:19,270
I would place everything

599
00:41:19,270 --> 00:41:20,220
in his hands.

600
00:41:23,430 --> 00:41:24,700
Yet he left before I could.

601
00:41:26,660 --> 00:41:27,620
Now that I think on it,

602
00:41:29,470 --> 00:41:30,430
how can I be sure

603
00:41:30,430 --> 00:41:31,500
that what I set out to do

604
00:41:33,660 --> 00:41:35,140
will never come to nothing?

605
00:41:39,310 --> 00:41:40,390
Flesh and blood

606
00:41:43,660 --> 00:41:45,020
can't withstand fate's turns.

607
00:41:53,310 --> 00:41:54,180
Duan Shunxi,

608
00:41:57,950 --> 00:41:59,700
your light will also fade one day.

609
00:42:00,990 --> 00:42:01,990
Fang Xianye

610
00:42:01,990 --> 00:42:03,100
only went before you.

611
00:42:07,140 --> 00:42:08,430
You're just a mortal.

612
00:42:10,870 --> 00:42:11,750
Look at me.

613
00:42:13,020 --> 00:42:14,390
I haven't learned to accept parting

614
00:42:14,390 --> 00:42:15,310
for 400 years.

615
00:42:21,470 --> 00:42:23,140
Fang Xianye died with no regrets

616
00:42:24,310 --> 00:42:25,310
but a clear conscience.

617
00:42:26,620 --> 00:42:27,540
He would not blame you.

618
00:42:29,390 --> 00:42:30,870
He'd be glad that he met you,

619
00:42:31,910 --> 00:42:33,430
so he could become himself again.

620
00:42:35,350 --> 00:42:36,660
Just remember him.

621
00:42:53,750 --> 00:42:54,590
(Fang Ji,)

622
00:42:56,580 --> 00:42:57,889
(in your next life, don't meet)

623
00:42:57,900 --> 00:42:59,140
(someone as troublesome as me.)

624
00:43:01,020 --> 00:43:01,950
(Live more lightly,)

625
00:43:04,270 --> 00:43:05,350
(and go find your own joy.)

626
00:43:13,200 --> 00:43:18,530
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

627
00:43:18,860 --> 00:43:23,110
♪Light encountered shadow♪

628
00:43:24,470 --> 00:43:29,840
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

629
00:43:30,140 --> 00:43:34,740
♪The unbreakable fate♪

630
00:43:35,830 --> 00:43:37,670
♪Suddenly cracked♪

631
00:43:49,880 --> 00:43:55,320
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

632
00:43:55,500 --> 00:43:59,830
♪Light encountered shadow♪

633
00:44:01,200 --> 00:44:06,590
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

634
00:44:06,820 --> 00:44:10,760
♪The unbreakable fate♪

635
00:44:12,530 --> 00:44:14,420
♪Suddenly cracked♪

636
00:44:17,080 --> 00:44:20,240
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

637
00:44:20,240 --> 00:44:22,770
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

638
00:44:22,770 --> 00:44:28,290
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

639
00:44:28,290 --> 00:44:31,530
♪Following fate's guidance♪

640
00:44:31,530 --> 00:44:36,390
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

641
00:44:36,730 --> 00:44:39,750
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

642
00:44:39,750 --> 00:44:42,570
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

643
00:44:42,830 --> 00:44:45,360
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

644
00:44:45,360 --> 00:44:50,780
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

645
00:44:50,950 --> 00:44:54,020
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

646
00:44:54,180 --> 00:44:59,080
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

647
00:44:59,290 --> 00:45:02,760
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

